    },
    {
      "start": 68.9,
      "end": 73.5,
      "text": "Make sure you approach every day, even when you've made it, in the same energy, passion,"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.8,
      "end": 74.3,
      "text": "and hunger."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.5,
      "end": 77.1,
      "text": "Because if you become complacent, that's the day you lose."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.4,
      "end": 77.9,
      "text": "You get comfortable."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.0,
      "end": 79.3,
      "text": "Somebody else is going to come take your business."
    },
    {
      "start": 79.6,
      "end": 81.5,
      "text": "Comfort is the most dangerous drug."
    },
    {
      "start": 81.8,
      "end": 84.3,
      "text": "An average is your biggest enemy to becoming success."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.6,
      "end": 85.1,
